<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Pamanekan ti email yo</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #4a5568; margin-bottom: 20px;">Pamanekan ti email address yo</h1>

  <p>Agyamanak gapu iti panagparehistro yo! Pangngaasi a pamanekan ti email address yo babaen ti panangpidut iti buton iti baba:</p>

  <div style="margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{ verificationUrl }}"
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;">
      Pamanekan ti Email
    </a>
  </div>

  <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 14px;">
    No saan nga agtrabaho ti buton, mabalin yo a kopiaen ken ipegket daytoy a link iti browser yo:
  </p>
  <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-all;">
    {{ verificationUrl }}
  </p>

  <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
    Agpaso daytoy a link iti 24 nga oras.
  </p>
</body>
</html>
